author: brane
msg: Prevent accessing freed memory through BDB environment batons by
invalidating the baton during pool cleanup of the environment
(svn_fs_bdb__open): Create the baton while the cache mutex is locked,
set the baton's 'valid' flag and register the invalidate_env_baton
cleanup in the environment descriptor's pool.
(svn_fs_bdb__close): Run the invalidate_env_baton cleanup when the
Don't touch the environment descriptor if the baton is invalid.
